<title>USA: Hayes Q3 net loss widens.</title>
<headline>Hayes Q3 net loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1996-11-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Net    loss		9,100     loss	 8,000</p>
<p> Revs			55,200		   72,300</p>
<p> Net inventory	   30,600		   40,000</p>
<p>	   9  MONTHS</p>
<p> Net    loss		  419     loss	10,700</p>
<p> Revs		     201,200		  197,000</p>
<p>(All data above 000s except per share numbers) Full company name is Hayes Microcomputer Products Inc</p>
<p>NOTE: In the third quarter 1996, results included a $6.5 million restructuring charge connected to a plant closure.</p>
<p>The company said the revenue decline in the third quarter 1996 was mostly because of lower prices and a downward revaluation of inventory.</p>
